Holly Gillibrand (amụrụ n'afọ 2005) bụ onye na-ahụ maka gburugburu ebe obibi na Scotland.Malite mgbe ọ dị afọ iri na atọ, ọ hapụrụ ụlọ akwụkwọ otu awa na Fraịdee ọ bụla dị ka akụkụ nke ọgbaghara ụlọ akwụkwọ maka ihu igwe. Ọ bụ onye nhazi maka Fraịdee maka ọdịnihu Scotland. O nwetara nkwado site na mgbasa ozi mmekọrịta.

A kpọrọ ya 2019 Glasgow Times Young Scotswoman of the Year. A kpọkwara ya otu n'ime ụmụ nwanyị iri atọ na-akpali akpali n'ihe ndepụta nke BBC's Woman's Hour Power List 2020 ma gbaa ya ajụjụ ọnụ na ihe ngosi ahụ. O dere maka Lochaber Times.
N'ọnwa Ọgọstụ 2020, Gillibrand kwadoro Chris Packham na mkpọsa mba nke ebumnuche ya bụ ịkwụsị mpụ anụ ọhịa
N'ọnwa Nọvemba nke afọ ahụ, ya na ndị ntorobịa ndị ọzọ nwere ajụjụ na azịza na Alok Sharma
Ọ na-eje ozi dị ka onye ndụmọdụ ndị ntorobịa maka ọrụ ebere Heal Rewilding, nke ebumnuche ya bụ iweghachi ala ọzọ na okike.
